RESERVED RIGHTS

The following are the exclusive property of the copyright holder
and are not licensed under any terms:

  - The name "Lorevox" and all associated brand names and marks
  - The name "Lori", the Lori interviewer persona, voice design,
    behavioral directives, and interview character
  - The Archive to History to Memoir three-layer architecture as
    expressed in this codebase
  - The runtime71 cognitive state system and its prompt composition
    pipeline
  - The multi-pass interview model (Pass 1, Pass 2A, Pass 2B)
    and the Timeline Spine structure
  - All prompt text, interview question sets, behavioral directive
    language, and system prompt templates
  - The memoir schema and biographical data structures
  - All documentation, design documents, and written materials
    in the docs/ directory

